Randall MILLER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2579 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. September 21, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel is dismissed as successive. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.141 (d)(6)(C).

SILBERMAN, BADALAMENTI, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
